question: give me the artist name with the most albums
initial_sql:
SELECT "Artist"."Name", COUNT("Album"."AlbumId") AS "AlbumCount"
FROM "Artist"
JOIN "Album" ON "Artist"."ArtistId" = "Album"."ArtistId"
GROUP BY "Artist"."Name"
ORDER BY "AlbumCount" DESC
LIMIT 1;
final_sql:
SELECT "Artist"."Name", COUNT("Album"."AlbumId") AS "AlbumCount"
FROM "Artist"
JOIN "Album" ON "Artist"."ArtistId" = "Album"."ArtistId"
GROUP BY "Artist"."Name"
ORDER BY "AlbumCount" DESC
LIMIT 1;
